Функции¶

stat_group¶
In [57]:
def stat_group(sign, x_0, _0, x_1, _1):
    """          .

         , 
                 (x_0  x_1),
          -  .
        , :
      ,     ..
    """
    pass
    d_0 = x_0.describe().reset_index()
    d_0.columns = [sign, _0]
    d_1 = x_1.describe().reset_index()
    d_1.columns = [sign, _1]
    d = pd.merge(d_0, d_1, left_on=sign, right_on=sign)
    display(d)
countplot_group¶
In [58]:
def countplot_group(x_0, _0, x_1, _1, X_name, Y_name, title):
    """          .
    
                 (x_0  x_1),
          -  .
        , :
      ,     ..,
      X  Y,  .
    """
    pass
    plt.subplots(figsize = (15,5))
    sns.countplot(x=x_0, color='Yellow', label=_0)
    sns.countplot(x=x_1, color='Green', label=_1, alpha=.66)
    sns.set_context(rc={'font.size':11})
    plt.xlabel(X_name)
    plt.ylabel(Y_name)
    plt.title(title)
    plt.legend();
